Information Science in a Ph.D. Computer Science Program This report contains recommendations on a sample course curriculum in the general area of information  organization and information system design in a Ph.D. Computer Science Program.  The subject area is  first briefly described, followed by a listing of some desirable graduate-level courses.  Suitable bibliographies  are appended. course curriculum, graduate courses, university courses,computer science curriculum, information  science, information organization, information retrieval, data retrieval, language analysis, information  processing 